Module lexakai.library
Package com.telenav.lexakai.library

Class Names

java.lang.Object
com.telenav.lexakai.library.Names
public class Names extends Object
This class contains utility methods for working with JavaParser names. Names can be produced with or without package qualification and with or without type parameters. The package name for a type can be deduced with packageName(String).
Author:
jonathanl (shibo)
